title: John McCormack - The Irish Minstrel
description:
John McCormack - The Irish Minstrel

HQ vinyl rip.  Ordered playlist and detailed tags.

This is an outstanding album which shows the versatility and skill of John McCormack.  The art songs are so beautiful they may make you cry.  Blast Morning for your school kids when you want them up.
